OL,3,CPizza shop fined after cockroaches
OL,4,Cfound in ice cream machine
OL,6,FA pizza shop has been prosecuted after
OL,7,Fit was found to have been infested
OL,8,Fwith cockroaches "at all stages of
OL,9,Ftheir lifecycle".
OL,11,FDuring a routine food inspection on 30
OL,12,FJanuary 2025 officers found that Pizza
OL,13,FRoma on Castle Street was "heavily
OL,14,Finfested" with cockroaches which were
OL,15,Ffound in the restaurant's ice cream
OL,16,Fmachine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
