OL,3,CPizza shop fined after cockroaches
OL,4,Cfound in ice cream machine
OL,6,FOfficers also found that the premises
OL,7,Fand equipment were dirty, food had
OL,8,Fbeen left out at room temperature, and
OL,9,Fthere was no effective food safety
OL,10,Fmanagement system in place.
OL,12,FAt Stockport Magistrates' Court,
OL,13,FTouseef Tajammul, who represented
OL,14,FPizza Roma XP Limited, pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto 11 food hygiene offences relating
OL,16,Fto Pizza Roma on Castle Street.
OL,18,FThe business received a number of
OL,19,Ffines amounting to more than #13,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
