OL,3,CPizza shop fined after cockroaches
OL,4,Cfound in ice cream machine
OL,6,FThe offences included the failure to
OL,7,Fdesign and maintain the premises to
OL,8,Fprevent pest infestation; to store
OL,9,Ffood and wrap materials safely; keep
OL,10,Fthe premises and equipment clean and
OL,11,Fin good repair; supervise and train
OL,12,Ffood handlers; register the food
OL,13,Fbusiness; and maintain adequate pest
OL,14,Fcontrol.
OL,16,FCllr Dan Oliver, Cabinet Member for
OL,17,FCommunities and Public Protection,
OL,18,Fcalled conditions at the takeaway
OL,19,F"completely unacceptable".J"They
OL,20,Frepresented a serious risk to public
OL,21,Fhealth," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
