OL,3,CPizza shop fined after cockroaches
OL,4,Cfound in ice cream machine
OL,6,F"This prosecution demonstrates our
OL,7,Fcommitment to ensuring food businesses
OL,8,Fmeet rigorous hygiene standards and
OL,9,Fthat customers can trust the safety of
OL,10,Fthe food they buy."
OL,12,F"We will continue to take firm action
OL,13,Fagainst businesses that fail to
OL,14,Fprotect the public."
OL,16,FThe business undertook a voluntary
OL,17,Fclosure on 30th January 2025 and was
OL,18,Freopened on 7th February 2025
OL,19,Ffollowing a full deep clean.
